        Swimming Pool Ownership and Selling a Brisbane Property
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Brisbane's climate makes a backyard pool usable for most of the year, and that lifestyle reality flows through to buyer perception and sale price. Here is how ongoing pool costs, condition, and presentation affect what your property actually achieves at sale.
      </p>
